column5: My oldest has asked me to join OFC, and without hesitation I allowed it. Her user name is SalmonSammy Many of you have met her in person or have seen her pics on a few of my threads. I can go on and about her and how many times Ive been outfished by her aswell. Beginners luck I say or Dad taught her well  Here is a favorite pic of mine from our quebec venture last month with leechman.  Heres to our newest member SalmonSammy
Hers her pic with the local mutt,lol
You realize she's going to tell us how many time she out fishes her oldman right?  LOL!!!!
More than likely Bill, she was taught to never lie . I should change my name to imdunfir
Welcome Sammy....You have a real cool dude for a dad.Hope you are as proud of him as he is of you.  And BTW, we like it when you kick his bum at fishing
Yup your done now Vince.  Welcome Samantha. We'll all have to do a Lake O, or Erie, fish this year.
Welcome aboard Sammy, look forward to some posts
Any girl who out fishes Jacques is very welcome.Perhaps the fishing reports will show much bigger fish  WELCOME
looking forward to some fishing reports SS
Welcome aboard  SalmonSammy don't be afraid to let us know how bad you beat your Dad & how you do it we can always use tips lol Tight Lines SBK
welcone aboard Sammy...thank the genetic gods you look nothin like your pop...pssst....thats a good thing...
Welcome to OFC Samantha    Glad you joined   Vinni... Nice pic   I have a similar pic on my computer   Your a funny guy Mike    but I like it
Welcome to the board SalmonSammy! Enjoy!
